text: Ceyco Georgia Zefanya (born 24 June 1999) is an Indonesian karateka. In 2018, she competed in the women's kumite 68 kg event at the 2018 Asian Games held in Jakarta, Indonesia without winning a medal. She was eliminated in her first match by Nguyễn Thị Ngoan of Vietnam. At the 2018 Asian Karate Championships held in Amman, Jordan, she won one of the bronze medals in the men's kumite 68 kg event.
